        "key": "轟閃落雷",
        "title": "轟閃落雷",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/464df75643b85d808ea7457d333c2520_1112953807423332196.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>普通攻擊</color>\n造成1點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": null
      },
      {
        "key": "霧虛之召",
        "title": "霧虛之召",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/ba8a520b631a5349ea54ca1fad2ec264_4673833156393734558.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n召喚 <color=#ffffff>雷螢</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>雷螢</color>\n<color=#ffd780>召喚物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>結束階段：</color> 造成1點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：3</color>\n<color=#ffffff>敵方累計打出3張行動牌後：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> +1。（最多疊加到3）\n<color=#ffffff>愚人眾·雷螢術士受到元素反應傷害後：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> -1。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "霆雷之護",
        "title": "霆雷之護",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/58e7aa03ca09a144cdac07649148383f_7108870071507844166.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成1點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> ，本角色 <color=#ffacff>附著雷元素</color> ，生成 <color=#ffffff>雷螢護罩</color> 並準備技能 <color=#ffffff>霆電迸發</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>雷螢護罩</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n為我方出戰角色提供 <color=#ffffff>1點護盾</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>建立時：</color> 如果我方場上存在 <color=#ffffff>雷螢</color> ，則額外提供其 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> 的 <color=#ffffff>護盾</color> 。（最多額外提供3點 <color=#ffffff>護盾</color> ）\n<color=#ffffff>霆電迸發</color>\n<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n（需準備1個行動輪）\n造成2點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷元素傷害",
        "title": "雷元素傷害",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/505a3ecf80d04b7ea2c46bc254e47f83_1891893807838200622.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超載</color> ：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超導</color> ：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>感電</color> ：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>原激化</color> ：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的 <color=#ffffff>[激化領域]</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷螢",
        "title": "雷螢",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/34858f53e503048f7850eb3a18565223_5009335896993109872.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>召喚物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>結束階段：</color> 造成1點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：3</color>\n<color=#ffffff>敵方累計打出3張行動牌後：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> +1。（最多疊加到3）\n<color=#ffffff>愚人眾·雷螢術士受到元素反應傷害後：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> -1。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "規則解釋",
        "title": "規則解釋",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/13/142453215/a45e27c2814a4cb2e60dbca70b6b53a8_3266233737044859891.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>護盾</color>\n此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color>\n此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> 耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
